ng mọi nhu c&acirc;̀u sử dụng của bạn với ba phi&ecirc;n bản b&ocirc;̣ nhớ là 64GB, 128GB và cao nh&acirc;́t là 256GB. Bạn có th&ecirc;̉ thỏa thích tải v&ecirc;̀ các ứng dụng c&ocirc;ng vi&ecirc;̣c, lưu trữ phim ảnh và tài li&ecirc;̣u quan trọng tr&ecirc;n iPhone 12 mini mà kh&ocirc;ng phải lo lắng v&ecirc;̀ dung lượng của máy.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"cpslazy loaded\" src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/mobile/apple/apple-iphone-12-mini-256gb-2.jpg\" alt=\"Dung lượng lưu trữ l&ecirc;n đ&ecirc;́n 256GB\" data-src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/mobile/apple/apple-iphone-12-mini-256gb-2.jpg\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" /></p>\r\n<p>iPhone 12 mini 256GB được trang bị vi&ecirc;n pin Li-Ion cho bạn thời gian sử dụng l&acirc;u d&agrave;i. Ngoài ra iPhone 12 mini còn h&ocirc;̃ trợ c&ocirc;ng ngh&ecirc;̣ sạc nhanh Power Delivery 2.0 20W, mang đ&ecirc;́n cho máy 50% pin sạc chỉ trong vòng 30 phút.</p>\r\n<p>T&acirc;́t nhi&ecirc;n kh&ocirc;ng th&ecirc;̉ thi&ecirc;́u c&ocirc;ng ngh&ecirc;̣ sạc nhanh kh&ocirc;ng d&acirc;y Qi 15W sẽ v&ocirc; cùng hữu ích n&ecirc;́u bạn đã có sẵn dock sạc kh&ocirc;ng d&acirc;y cho iPhone.</p>\r\n<h3>Màn hình 5.4 inch, vi xử lý A14 Bionic&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<p>iPhone 12 mini 256GB được trang bị màn hình kích thước 5.4 inch, đ&ocirc;̣ ph&acirc;n giải Full HD+ (2340 x 1080 pixels).</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"cpslazy loaded\" src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/mobile/apple/apple-iphone-12-mini-256gb-chinh-hang-vna-2.jpg\" alt=\"Màn hình 5.4 inch\" data-src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/mobile/apple/apple-iphone-12-mini-256gb-chinh-hang-vna-2.jpg\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" /></p>\r\n<p>iPhone 12 mini 256GB được sản xu&acirc;́t tr&ecirc;n ti&ecirc;́n trình 5nm, đi kèm với chip c&acirc;́u hình Apple GPU 4 lõi sẽ mang đ&ecirc;́n hi&ecirc;̣u năng mạnh nh&acirc;́t</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"cpslazy loaded\" src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/mobile/apple/apple-iphone-12-mini-256gb-1.jpg\" alt=\"v&acirc;̣n hành mạng 5G\" data-src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/mobile/apple/apple-iphone-12-mini-256gb-1.jpg\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" /></p>', 'trắng,đen', NULL, '25990000', '25000000', '25000000', 'https://youtu.be/HvTU_HEDfeI', 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, NULL, 0, '[\"\\/media\\/products\\/1616421169.jpg\",\"\\/media\\/products\\/1616421172.jpg\",\"\\/media\\/products\\/1616421174.jpg\",\"\\/media\\/products\\/1616421178.jpg\"]', 1, '2021-03-22 13:55:14', NULL),
