h&ocirc;ng th&acirc;́m m&ocirc;̀ h&ocirc;i khi đeo tr&ecirc;n tay trong thời gian dài.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"cpslazy loaded\" src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/accessories/watch_band/apple-watch-series-6-44mm-4g-vien-thep-day-thep-1.jpg\" alt=\"Thi&ecirc;́t k&ecirc;́ vi&ecirc;̀n thép cùng d&acirc;y đeo thép tăng th&ecirc;m vẻ ngoài sang trọng\" data-src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/accessories/watch_band/apple-watch-series-6-44mm-4g-vien-thep-day-thep-1.jpg\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" /></p>\r\n<p>Apple Watch Series 6 44mm được tích hợp c&ocirc;ng ngh&ecirc;̣ mạng 4G. Đi&ecirc;̀u này cho phép người dùng lắp SIM 4G vào và k&ecirc;́t n&ocirc;́i internet trực ti&ecirc;́p tr&ecirc;n smartwatch cho các tính năng b&ocirc;̉ trợ hữu ích.</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Theo dẽo nhịp tim, đo ECG và nhi&ecirc;̀u ch&ecirc;́ đ&ocirc;̣ sức khỏe b&ecirc;n trong</strong></h3>\r\n<p>Apple Watch Series 6 44mm 4G vi&ecirc;̀n thép d&acirc;y thép được tích hợp ch&ecirc;́ đ&ocirc;̣ đo ECG - đo lường chỉ s&ocirc;́ đi&ecirc;̣n t&acirc;m đ&ocirc;̀ hi&ecirc;̣n đại. Tính năng này ph&acirc;n tích đi&ecirc;̣n cực cùng cảm bi&ecirc;́n đ&ecirc;̉ hi&ecirc;̉n thị th&ocirc;ng s&ocirc;́ nhịp tim b&ecirc;n trong cơ th&ecirc;̉ bạn, giúp bạn ch&acirc;̉n đoán được các b&ecirc;̣nh li&ecirc;n quan đ&ecirc;́n tim và khám ngay khi c&acirc;̀n thi&ecirc;́t.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"cpslazy loaded\" src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/accessories/watch_band/apple-watch-series-6-44mm-4g-vien-thep-day-thep-2_1.jpg\" alt=\"Đo chỉ s&ocirc;́ &ocirc;xy trong máu, đo ECG và nhi&ecirc;̀u ch&ecirc;́ đ&ocirc;̣ sức khỏe b&ecirc;n trong\" data-src=\"https://cdn.cellphones.com.vn/media/wysiwyg/accessories/watch_band/apple-watch-series-6-44mm-4g-vien-thep-day-thep-2_1.jpg\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" /></p>\r\n<p>Các ch&ecirc;́ đ&ocirc;̣ sức khỏe có tr&ecirc;n Apple Watch Series 6 44mm 4G g&ocirc;̀m có đạp xe, nhảy xa, bơi l&ocirc;̣i, cardio, cùng nhi&ecirc;̀u ch&ecirc;́ đ&ocirc;̣ th&ecirc;̉ thao ph&ocirc;̉ bi&ecirc;́n hi&ecirc;̣n nay. Các chỉ s&ocirc;́ v&ecirc;̀ nhịp tim, thời gian t&acirc;̣p, quãng đường đã đi, t&ocirc;́c đ&ocirc;̣ t&acirc;̣p luy&ecirc;̣n đ&ecirc;̀u được ghi chú &amp; hi&ecirc;̉n thị rõ nét tr&ecirc;n màn hình Retina sắc nét.</p>', 'đen,bạc', NULL, '22990000', '20000000', '20000000', 'https://youtu.be/n6LXqRNTzuE', 0, 0, 1, 0, 1, NULL, 0, '[\"\\/media\\/products\\/1616593719.jpg\",\"\\/media\\/products\\/1616593722.jpg\",\"\\/media\\/products\\/1616593724.jpg\",\"\\/media\\/products\\/1616593726.jpg\"]', 1, '2021-03-24 13:53:42', NULL);
